Package: ggvis
Title: Interactive grammar of graphics
Description: ggvis implements a interactive grammar of graphics, taking the
    best parts of ggplot2, combining them with shiny's reactive framework and
    drawing web graphics using vega.
Version: 0.3.0.99
Author: RStudio, Inc.
Maintainer: Winston Chang <winston@rstudio.com>
URL: http://ggvis.rstudio.com/
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
    assertthat,
    RJSONIO,
    shiny (>= 0.10),
    magrittr,
    dplyr (>= 0.2),
    htmltools (>= 0.2.4),
    plyr
Suggests:
    MASS,
    mgcv,
    testthat (>= 0.8.1),
    knitr (>= 1.6),
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
